    </a>
  </h2>

          <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Ads info</button>
        </li>
          <button type="button" class="dropdown-link js-action-dismiss">
            I don't like this ad
          </button>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">We're sorry for anyone in Rugby &amp; certain areas in B'ham who currently have no water or poor pressure. The thaw has caused unprecedented amounts of leaks &amp; is causing problems on our network. Were working to get everyone back on supply but this is going to take some time. Sorry!</p>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">There has been no specific proposal - as yet - from the EU to ban straws. The EU has promised analytical work on the scope of a legislative initiative to reduce single use plastics. Also waiting for the EU to catch up on microbeads - UKs ban is 1st in Europe <a href="/hashtag/greenbrexit?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>greenbrexit</b></a><a href="https://t.co/Ohplb3ZtXt" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/timmermanseu/status/966996904847532033" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/timmermanseu/status/966996904847532033"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/timmermanseu/s</span><span class="invisible">tatus/966996904847532033</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

These are not cheap, quite often the sums would take years for the average person to earn. People want to know that their money is being spent properly &amp; not used to keep people quiet<a href="https://t.co/dhYAO1Iti3" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/dhYAO1Iti3</a></p>

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">The statistics released today show a 4% decrease in rough sleeping in the <a href="/WestMids_CA" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="3414955703"><s>@</s><b>WestMids_CA</b></a> area against a national increase. Even one rough sleeper is one too many. However, it points towards the success of our local authorities and third sector and the value of collaboration.</p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">In 2015 we introduced the 5p charge on plastic carrier bags, we now see 9bn fewer bags being used. It's making a real difference. We want to do the same with single use plastics. Nobody who watched <a href="/hashtag/BluePlanet2?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>BluePlanet2</b></a> will doubt the need for us to do something - and we will. <a href="/hashtag/Marr?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Marr</b></a></p>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Theresa May Retweeted Cleaner Seas Project</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Eight million tonnes of plastic makes its way into the worlds seas and oceans each year - our government will do all it can to play its part in stopping this. The work of <a href="/BudeCleanerSeas" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1479474223"><s>@</s><b>BudeCleanerSeas</b></a> is vital to that ambition. Do follow and support their work, as <a href="/scottmann4NC" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="112761860"><s>@</s><b>scottmann4NC</b></a> does:<a href="https://t.co/UDYz0jow9V" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/budecleanerseas/status/947550970996719616" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/budecleanerseas/status/947550970996719616"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/budecleanersea</span><span class="invisible">s/status/947550970996719616</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Great news for Birmingham and the West Midlands!<a href="https://t.co/kDumIHcqCb" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/andy4wm/status/943776241710223360" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/andy4wm/status/943776241710223360"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/andy4wm/status</span><span class="invisible">/943776241710223360</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">I will work alongside Jean Templeton from <a href="/StBasilsCharity" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="59754180"><s>@</s><b>StBasilsCharity</b></a> who chairs the West Midlands Homelessness Task Force. </div>

This is a time of huge celebration for two people in love and, on behalf of myself, the Government and the country, I wish them great happiness for the future.<a href="https://t.co/Sfx76X98BW" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/clarencehouse/status/935085955383427072" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/clarencehouse/status/935085955383427072"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/clarencehouse/</span><span class="invisible">status/935085955383427072</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

        <span class="u-hiddenVisually">More</span>
      </div>
  </button>
  <div class="dropdown-menu is-autoCentered">

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>

</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Emma Crane Retweeted Vote 100</p>

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">For Britain to succeed, we need to unleash the ability of every person.           <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">Out with <span class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="711222979959644161"><s>@</s><b>SandwellTories</b></span> for <span class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1898071255"><s>@</s><b>DocHardie</b></span> in sunny Tipton this afternoon.   </div>
